<bibRefCitation author="Lepeletier, A. L. M." box="[277,472,1989,2015]" pageId="10" pageNumber="33" refId="ref10183" refString="Lepeletier, A. L. M. (1841) Histoire Naturelle des Insectes. Hymenopteres. Vol. 2. Roret, Paris, 680 pp." type="book" year="1841">Lepeletier (1841)</bibRefCitation>
