<typeStatus box="[996,1099,189,215]" pageId="11" pageNumber="34">lectotype</typeStatus>
designation. The specimen he studied has the following data label: 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Lepeletier" authorityYear="1841" box="[563,670,225,251]" class="Insecta" family="Apidae" genus="Centris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="11" pageNumber="34" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="pulverata">
